headline: Pinnacle Financial Partners Lands in Top 5 Best Workplaces for Women
summary: NASHVILLE, Tenn,, October 23, 2025--Pinnacle Financial Partners rose into the top five nationwide in FORTUNE magazine’s 2025 list of the Best Workplaces for Women. This is the firm’s eighth time being named to this prestigious list, this year coming in at No. 4, up from No. 8 in 2024. Pinnacle also earned this distinction in 2023, 2022, 2021, 2020, 2018 and 2017.

headline: City of Los Angeles, LA Nonprofits Partner with Cisco to Launch New Community Wi-Fi
summary: Today, Cisco (NASDAQ: CSCO) alongside government and nonprofit partners including the City of Los Angeles, Destination Crenshaw, the California Community Foundation, and Digital Equity LA announce a new community Wi-Fi initiative that will provide free internet access along major streets, parks and public gathering places in LA's historic Crenshaw Corridor.

headline: Cisco unveils immersive AI security operations centre showcase to help prepare organizations from future threats
summary: Marking Cybersecurity Awareness Month, Cisco – the worldwide leader in networking and security – has launched its AI-Powered Security Operations Centre (SOC) showcase at the Toronto Innovation Centre. The new initiative is designed to demonstrate the future of intelligent cyber defence for Canadian organizations.
